_sText: The second version of my first map de_centre_building. A different skybox, a light_env and a sun has been added. As a result more lights and nice looking shadows and lights, some of which flicker creating a nice affect. I would like to put a big thanks to teshok for his advice on shybox's. Also i would like to say that i think 3kliksphillip is an extremely good mapper and creates amazing tutorials. His tutorials can be found on youtube.
